00:42:31,049 --> 00:42:33,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak mungkin mimpi. Ini terasa sangat nyata.</font>

657
00:42:42,199 --> 00:42:43,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku di kampus?</font>

658
00:42:55,409 --> 00:42:56,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Jin Joo,</font>

659
00:42:58,449 --> 00:43:00,350
