<font color=#FFFF00>memang menyenangkan.</font>

684
00:45:37,980 --> 00:45:39,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Choi Ban Do?</font>

685
00:45:42,880 --> 00:45:44,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Ma Jin Joo?</font>

