00:47:41,270 --> 00:47:42,770
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bubar, jalan./- Bubar, jalan.</font>

711
00:47:46,540 --> 00:47:48,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, lihat itu.</font>

712
00:47:49,569 --> 00:47:51,739
